```plantuml
@startuml ashavijit_Face-Find

actor User
participant "Frontend (Bootstrap)" as Frontend
participant "Django View" as View
participant "Django Model" as Model
participant "Azure Face API" as AzureAPI
participant "Email Service" as Email

User -> Frontend: Submits Missing Person Form
Frontend -> View: POST request with form data
View -> Model: save(missing_person_data)
Model --> View: MissingPerson instance
View -> AzureAPI: generateFaceId(photo)
AzureAPI --> View: face_id
View -> Model: update(missing_person.face_id)
View -> Email: send_confirmation(user_email)
Email --> View: success
View --> Frontend: success response
Frontend --> User: confirmation message

User -> Frontend: Submits Reported Person Form
Frontend -> View: POST request with form data
View -> Model: save(reported_person_data)
Model --> View: ReportedPerson instance
View -> AzureAPI: generateFaceId(photo)
AzureAPI --> View: face_id
View -> Model: update(reported_person.face_id)
View -> Model: findPotentialMatches(face_id)
Model -> AzureAPI: findSimilarFaces(face_id)
AzureAPI --> Model: potential_matches
Model --> View: match_results
View -> Email: send_match_notification(contact_email)
Email --> View: success
View --> Frontend: success response
Frontend --> User: confirmation message

@enduml
```